<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="mb-5 to-edge-right to-edge-left">
    <%= content_tag :div, nil, class: 'video-hero', data: {
        video: image_path('services/hero/hero.mp4'),
        slides: [{
          image:    image_path('services/hero/1.jpg'),
          caption:  'New Construction',
          href:     '#new-construction',
          time:     7,
        },{
          image:    image_path('services/hero/2.jpg'),
          caption:  'Custom Home Building',
          href:     '#new-construction',
          time:     15,
        },{
          image:    image_path('services/hero/3.jpg'),
          caption:  'Restoration',
          href:     '#remodeling',
          time:     21,
        },{
          image:    image_path('services/hero/4.jpg'),
          caption:  'Complete Home Renovation',
          href:     '#remodeling',
          time:     28,
        }].to_json
      } %>
  </div>

  <div class="anchor" id="new-construction"></div>

  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2 class="h5 text-uppercase hul">
        <small>New Construction</small>
      </h2>

      <p><em>
        From design through completion our qualified crew is dedicated to
        helping you with every step of the way!
      </em></p>

      <p>
        Our many choices make it easy to choose a
        <a href="#">model</a>
        which best suits you. With Shemss flexibility, unique options, and
        finishing touches, it has never been easier to find a perfect home.
        We’ll guide you through the various unique stages of building a new
        construction home. From selecting a model, finding the perfect lot,
        securing financing, design, and construction.
      </p>

      <p>
        Building beautiful homes is our line of expertise and passion. We hope
        that our enthusiasm makes your dream home journey incredible.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you’re looking for simplicity and elegance, consider a
        Modern/Contemporary home with strong geometric shapes and an open floor
        plan.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-5">
      <div class="text-white bg-dark p-3 p-sm-4 to-edge-right">
        <h2 class="h5 text-uppercase hul"><small>Our Process</small></h2>

        <p><em>
          We believe that collaboration between our team and the client is
          essential for a successful outcome.
        </em></p>

        <p>
          With an open dialogue and clear communication, it’s an easy and
          enjoyable process, especially when realizing the vision of your dream
          home is coming to life. We’re open to let you be as “hands-on” or as
          “hands-off” as you wish.
        </p>

        <p>
          We offer a free consultation to help you feel assured that a Shemss
          home is perfect for you. If you decide to work with us we have a
          streamlined process to make your journey one that’s low stress and
          positive experience.
        </p>

        <ul class="text-uppercase">
          <li>Preliminary Schematic Design &amp; Budgeting</li>
          <li>Design Detail &amp; Permit Applications</li>
          <li>Scheduling</li>
          <li>Construction</li>
          <li>Completion</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-md-5">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg mb-5 process-col">
      <svg class="img-fluid mb-4 process-icon">
        <%= tag :use, ->(href) { { href: href, 'xlink:href': href} }
          .call(image_path 'services/process.svg#schematic') %>
      </svg>

      <h4 class="h6 text-uppercase">
        Preliminary Schematic Design &amp; Budgeting
      </h4>

      <p><em>
        In this phase we lay the groundwork to kick-start your project into
        action.
      </em></p>

      <p>Steps include:</p>

      <p>
        Highlight project goals and the general scope of work, Establish a
        preliminary schematic design, Devise the floor and site plan, and Review
        budget allocation. At this point, we sign a contract to move forward
        with the project.
      </p>

      <p>At this point, we sign a contract to move forward with the project.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg mb-5 process-col">
      <svg class="img-fluid mb-4 process-icon">
        <%= tag :use, ->(href) { { href: href, 'xlink:href': href} }
          .call(image_path 'services/process.svg#detail') %>
      </svg>

      <h4 class="h6 text-uppercase">Design Detail &amp; Permit Applications</h4>

      <p><em>Let’s get this party started: In this phase the fun begins.</em></p>

      <p>
        We will do fine tuning and detailing of the schematic design, creating a
        final master plan. Select materials and fixtures that reflect your
        taste. Prepare and submit construction and engineering documents to the
        appropriate city/county departments.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg mb-5 process-col">
      <svg class="img-fluid mb-4 process-icon">
        <%= tag :use, ->(href) { { href: href, 'xlink:href': href} }
          .call(image_path 'services/process.svg#scheduling') %>
      </svg>

      <h4 class="h6 text-uppercase">Scheduling</h4>

      <p><em>
        With permit in hand it’s time to arrange all the details and fast-track
        the project.
      </em></p>

      <p>
        Subcontractors and craftsmen will be scheduled, material procurement
        will be done, and the project timeline will be reviewed.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg mb-5 process-col">
      <svg class="img-fluid mb-4 process-icon">
        <%= tag :use, ->(href) { { href: href, 'xlink:href': href} }
          .call(image_path 'services/process.svg#construction') %>
      </svg>

      <h4 class="h6 text-uppercase">Construction</h4>

      <p><em>Where your dream home meets reality.</em></p>

      <p>
        We will ensure that site preparation is complete, material delivered,
        hands-on project management will ensure adherence to timeline. Careful
        supervision of all moving parts to ensure the highest quality of
        workmanship performed by our trade professionals.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg mb-5 process-col">
      <svg class="img-fluid mb-4 process-icon">
        <%= tag :use, ->(href) { { href: href, 'xlink:href': href} }
          .call(image_path 'services/process.svg#completion') %>
      </svg>

      <h4 class="h6 text-uppercase">Completion</h4>

      <p><em>Time flies when you’re having fun.</em></p>

      <p>
        24 weeks go by in the blink of an eye! Our work is done and we hand you
        the keys! Many of our clients have become good friends as we have taken
        the construction journey together. We wish you much joy and happiness in
        your home.
      </p>

      <p>
        Shemss stands proudly behind the quality and durability of their work.
        For this reason, we offer a fully comprehensive warranty on our homes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mt-md-3 mt-lg-0 mb-5 built-to-evolve">
    <div class="col-md col-lg-5 mb-md-5">
      <div class="vertical-center">
        <div class="text-white bg-dark p-3 p-sm-5 p-md-4 to-edge-left to-edge-right pad-edge vertical-center-inner">
