        building a new home means is moving towards the future! Gone with
        delays, stress, red tape, hidden costs, and confusion. We provide a
        simple path to an affordable thoughtfully designed home. Shemss homes
        are built to last, They’re functional, smart, easy to maintain and ready
        to tackle this new millennium.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md col-lg-5 mb-md-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm col-md-12 col-lg">
          <div class="mt-3 mt-md-0 mb-3">
            <div class="clock-face">
              <div class="clock-outer">
                <div class="clock-inner">
                  <div class="hours-container">
                    <div class="hours"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="minutes-container">
